      "side": 1,
      "message": "`server_config` is a non-loading Cache; `memoryLimit \u003d 0` relies on Caffeine\u0027s weight-based eviction (entries evicted asynchronously immediately after insert) rather than the cleaner `PassthroughLoadingCache` shortcut that applies to `LoadingCache` instances.\n\nThere is a small race window where a stale entry may be returned before async eviction, but in practice this is sufficient to mitigate Issue 514817934.",
